---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Cloud Architecture | Muhammad Kurnia Sani">
    <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 sm:py-24">
        <header class="max-w-2xl mb-16">
            <h1
                class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl"
            >
                Cloud Infrastructure
            </h1>
            <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                To ensure a secure, low-latency, and high-performance experience
                globally, I architected this portfolio using a cloud-native
                approach on AWS.
            </p>
        </header>

        <section class="mb-20">
            <div
                class="rounded-2xl p-2 sm:p-4 bg-[#0f172a] border border-slate-200 shadow-xl overflow-hidden"
            >
                <img
                    src="https://dpgb1j61mlyva.cloudfront.net/aws-architecture.webp"
                    alt="AWS Architecture Diagram showing S3, CloudFront, and WAF"
                    class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl"
                />
            </div>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-500 flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg
                    class="w-4 h-4"
                    fill="none"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                >
                    <path
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
                    ></path>
                </svg>
                System diagram illustrating the global content delivery network.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2
                class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mb-8"
            >
                Key Components
            </h2>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div
                    class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/50 hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors"
                >
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                        <div class="p-2 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 rounded-lg">
                            <svg
                                class="w-5 h-5"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                ><path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9"
                                ></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900">
                            Amazon CloudFront
                        </h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-2">
                        <strong>Role:</strong> Content delivery and global caching.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
                        <strong>Benefit:</strong> Serving assets from the Jakarta
                        (CGK) edge location drastically reduces latency for local
                        users, while providing instant global reach to European servers.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div
                    class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/50 hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors"
                >
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                        <div class="p-2 bg-green-50 text-green-600 rounded-lg">
                            <svg
                                class="w-5 h-5"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                ><path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M4 7v10c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4V7M4 7c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4M4 7c0-2.21 3.582-4 8-4s8 1.79 8 4m0 5c0 2.21-3.582 4-8 4s-8-1.79-8-4"
                                ></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Amazon S3</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-2">
                        <strong>Role:</strong> Secure object storage for static assets.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
                        <strong>Region:</strong> Hosted in <code
                            >ap-southeast-3</code
                        > (Jakarta) to comply with data residency preferences and
                        optimize regional load times.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div
                    class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/50 hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors"
                >
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                        <div
                            class="p-2 bg-purple-50 text-purple-600 rounded-lg"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-5 h-5"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                ><path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"
                                ></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900">
                            Origin Access Control (OAC)
                        </h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-2">
                        <strong>The Architect's Choice:</strong> Instead of relying
                        on public buckets, OAC was implemented.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
                        This ensures that S3 content is strictly accessible only
                        via the CloudFront distribution, preventing unauthorized
                        direct origin access.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div
                    class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/50 hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors"
                >
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                        <div class="p-2 bg-red-50 text-red-600 rounded-lg">
                            <svg
                                class="w-5 h-5"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                ><path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"
                                ></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900">AWS WAF</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-2">
                        <strong>Role:</strong> Perimeter security.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
                        Integrated Web Application Firewall to protect the CDN
                        against common web vulnerabilities, DDoS attempts, and
                        malicious bots.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</BaseLayout>
